Comment: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,關鍵幀標題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:52.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}とうに死んだ心と　止まない雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:57.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}血溜まりで泣いている　天使と出逢った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:03.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}まだ救いを信じる　キミの細い声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:08.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}わたしを魔王にするのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}ヒカリナキセカイ　生き抜く強さを頂戴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}神様なんて人でなしから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}キミを守れるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:28.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}雷槌が　いま　わたしを撃ち抜いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:34.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}この愛で　いま　わたしは修羅に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:39.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}雷槌のように　生命よ　煌めいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}全てを燃やし尽くして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}キミの未来を照らし　そして　消える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}「愚かな人間だったよ」と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}いつか　そう　笑ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&\fscx65\fscy65\pos(917,1002)}ひと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:52.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}在倾盆的雨下 怀着死去的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:57.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}却相遇那天使 在血泊中哀鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:03.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}你那空灵嗓音 让我仍信救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:08.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}使我登上了魔王的宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}请赐我在无光世界 得以生存之力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}可怎能奢求众神散发人性光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.03,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}不如让我来守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:28.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}让那天雷 现在 将我整个贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:34.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}以这份爱 现在 让我化身修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:39.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}如惊雷划破天空 让生命灿烂辉煌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}直至燃尽所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.46,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}用尽余晖照亮你的未来 最终黯淡消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}“区区愚蠢的人类”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.39,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\xbord1\shad1\blur20\3a&H30&\4a&H30&}就让他们 笑到最后吧
